== Jacked ==

The word Jacked in slang references, may either mean for someone to be, not only strong, but having muscles showing, or for someone to of stolen an object.

== Jacked as in Strong ==

The term Jacked when saying someone is strong, makes a true reference to someone on steriods, although it is usually just mean to indicate strength. Especially if someones veins are showing more than usual, not due to a illness. An example of how this would be used is: "Wow, that guy is jacked!" Jacked may also go together with ripped, describing someone who has very showing abodomial mucles.

== Jacked as in to Steal ==

Some people use the word Jacked to mean steal. As in "Dude, he just jacked my bike!" Although this phrase is used rarely, it may be found used among a younger population.